WEBVTT

00:00.495 --> 00:01.437
Hello, friends.

00:01.693 --> 00:04.281
Today, we'll learn about the Stone Age.

00:04.601 --> 00:08.103
The Stone Age is a very ancient period of human history...

00:08.409 --> 00:11.947
...when people used weapons and tools made of stone.

00:12.591 --> 00:18.421
The Stone Age is a period of history in which humans used primitive stone tools.

00:18.691 --> 00:21.027
Lasting about two and a half million years,...

00:21.300 --> 00:24.817
...the Stone Age ended approximately 5,000 years ago...

00:25.090 --> 00:28.500
...when humans in the Near East began working with metal.

00:29.161 --> 00:32.349
This age is the first period of human history,...

00:32.600 --> 00:36.465
...so people from the Stone Age were the first to create clothing.

00:36.952 --> 00:41.168
People wore clothes made of animal skins during the winter months,...

00:41.429 --> 00:45.798
...and clothes built from grass and bark of trees during the summers.

